{"id":3834,"date":"2019-09-06T12:15:16","date_gmt":"2019-09-06T05:15:16","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/tintuc8.muathemewordpress.net\/?p=3834"},"modified":"2021-05-25T20:31:54","modified_gmt":"2021-05-25T13:31:54","slug":"dat-tu-lanh-the-nao-cho-hop-phong-thuy-ban-nen-biet","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/tintuc6.webtudong8giay.com\/dat-tu-lanh-the-nao-cho-hop-phong-thuy-ban-nen-biet\/","title":{"rendered":"\u0110\u1eb7t t\u1ee7 l\u1ea1nh th\u1ebf n\u00e0o cho h\u1ee3p phong th\u1ee7y b\u1ea1n n\u00ean bi\u1ebft"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><strong>\u0110\u1eb7t t\u1ee7 l\u1ea1nh \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed b\u1ea5t ti\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 g\u00e2y m\u1ea5t m\u1ef9 quan c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 b\u1ebfp m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn gia ch\u1ee7 theo phong th\u1ee7y.<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Hi\u1ec7n nay, h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 gia \u0111\u00ecnh n\u00e0o c\u0169ng c\u00f3 t\u1ee7 l\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng m\u00e0 n\u00f3 mang l\u1ea1i cho cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u00edt ai bi\u1ebft hay quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb7t t\u1ee7 l\u1ea1nh \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0o m\u1edbi h\u1ee3p phong th\u1ee7y.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/kientrucvietnam.org.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/dat-tu-lanh-the-nao-cho-hop-phong-thuy-gia-dinh-am-em.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-39162\" src=\"http:\/\/kientrucvietnam.org.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/dat-tu-lanh-the-nao-cho-hop-phong-thuy-gia-dinh-am-em.jpg\" alt=\"dat-tu-lanh-the-nao-cho-hop-phong-thuy-gia-dinh-am-em\" width=\"567\" height=\"425\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady, n\u1ebfu ch\u1eb3ng may \u0111\u1eb7t t\u1ee7 l\u1ea1nh \u1edf nh\u1eefng n\u01a1i ki\u00eang k\u1ef5 s\u1ebd c\u00f2n mang l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng may cho gia ch\u1ee7, l\u00e0m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong gia \u0111\u00ecnh. V\u1eady trong phong th\u1ee7y, \u0111\u1eb7t t\u1ee7 l\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o m\u1edbi \u0111\u00fang?<\/p>\n<p><strong>1. T\u1ed1t\u00a0nh\u1ea5t n\u00ean \u0111\u1eb7t t\u1ee7 l\u1ea1nh \u1edf nh\u00e0 b\u1ebfp<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>T\u1ee7 l\u1ea1nh thu\u1ed9c h\u00e0nh Kim, c\u00f2n b\u1ebfp thu\u1ed9c h\u00e0nh H\u1ecfa, n\u01a1i v\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u1ecfa th\u00ec c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Kim \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng. B\u1edfi v\u00ec H\u1ecfa kh\u1eafc Kim\u00a0n\u00ean s\u1ebd ti\u1ebft ch\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh H\u1ecfa \u1edf kh\u00f4ng gian n\u00e0y. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec\u00a0th\u1ebf, \u0111\u1eb7t t\u1ee7 l\u1ea1nh \u1edf trong nh\u00e0 b\u1ebfp l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/kientrucvietnam.org.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/dat-tu-lanh-the-nao-cho-hop-phong-thuy-gia-dinh-am-em-hinh-2.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-39163\" src=\"http:\/\/kientrucvietnam.org.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/dat-tu-lanh-the-nao-cho-hop-phong-thuy-gia-dinh-am-em-hinh-2.jpg\" alt=\"dat-tu-lanh-the-nao-cho-hop-phong-thuy-gia-dinh-am-em-hinh-2\" width=\"567\" height=\"424\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p><strong>2. Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t t\u1ee7 l\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n ho\u1eb7c qu\u00e1 g\u1ea7n b\u1ebfp<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a t\u1ee7 l\u1ea1nh l\u00e0 \u1edf nh\u00e0 b\u1ebfp, song kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00ea t\u1ee7 l\u1ea1nh qu\u00e1 g\u1ea7n b\u1ebfp n\u1ea5u hay \u1edf ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n.<\/p>\n<p>L\u00fd gi\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, l\u00e0 v\u00ec kh\u00ed n\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ebfp khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1ecfa ra v\u00e0 h\u01a1i l\u1ea1nh t\u1eeb t\u1ee7 l\u1ea1nh l\u00e0 xung kh\u1eafc v\u1edbi nhau qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd g\u00e2y \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u1ee7a gia ch\u1ee7. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady, theo\u00a0phong th\u1ee7y nh\u00e0 b\u1ebfp th\u00ec c\u00e1ch b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o g\u00e2y ra s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng thu\u1eadn h\u00f2a, hay c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn trong gia \u0111\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/kientrucvietnam.org.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/dat-tu-lanh-the-nao-cho-hop-phong-thuy-gia-dinh-am-em-hinh-3.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-39164\" src=\"http:\/\/kientrucvietnam.org.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/dat-tu-lanh-the-nao-cho-hop-phong-thuy-gia-dinh-am-em-hinh-3.jpg\" alt=\"dat-tu-lanh-the-nao-cho-hop-phong-thuy-gia-dinh-am-em-hinh-3\" width=\"567\" height=\"359\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p><strong>3. H\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1eb7t t\u1ee7 l\u1ea1nh trong ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>C\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u gia \u0111\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t trong nh\u00e0 b\u1ebfp m\u1ed9t t\u1ee7 l\u1ea1nh r\u1ed3i, nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i c\u00f2n \u0111\u1eb7t th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i n\u1eefa \u1edf ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ti\u1ec7n th\u00ec c\u00f3 ti\u1ec7n nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i k\u1ef5 v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1ec7nh Kim.<\/p>\n<p>Nh\u01b0 ban \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, t\u1ee7 l\u1ea1nh thu\u1ed9c h\u00e0nh Kim, n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c t\u0103ng Kim trong nh\u00e0 s\u1ebd d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eadn hung, gia ch\u1ee7 d\u1ec5 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng may.<\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i b\u1edbt \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y m\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t t\u1ee7 l\u1ea1nh \u1edf ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 cho t\u1ee7 l\u1ea1nh v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u1ee7 g\u1ed7.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/kientrucvietnam.org.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/dat-tu-lanh-the-nao-cho-hop-phong-thuy-gia-dinh-am-em-hinh-4.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-39165\" src=\"http:\/\/kientrucvietnam.org.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/dat-tu-lanh-the-nao-cho-hop-phong-thuy-gia-dinh-am-em-hinh-4.jpg\" alt=\"dat-tu-lanh-the-nao-cho-hop-phong-thuy-gia-dinh-am-em-hinh-4\" width=\"567\" height=\"850\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p><strong>4. Tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ee7 l\u1ea1nh ch\u00e9o ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n c\u1eeda ra v\u00e0o<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Trong phong th\u1ee7y, t\u1ee7\u00a0l\u1ea1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 \u201cT\u00e0i kh\u1ed1\u201d, t\u1ee9c kho c\u1ee7a. N\u00ean khi \u0111\u1eb7t t\u1ee7 l\u1ea1nh trong ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch, tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t t\u1ee7 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00e9o v\u1edbi c\u1eeda ra v\u00e0o; c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean \u0111\u1eb7t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n. Nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn t\u00e0i l\u1ed9c, c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3i trong gia \u0111\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh; th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n l\u00e0m hao t\u00e0i kh\u00ed, th\u1ea5t tho\u00e1t ti\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a, c\u00f4ng danh \u0111i xu\u1ed1ng.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/kientrucvietnam.org.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/dat-tu-lanh-the-nao-cho-hop-phong-thuy-gia-dinh-am-em-hinh-5.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-39166\" src=\"http:\/\/kientrucvietnam.org.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/dat-tu-lanh-the-nao-cho-hop-phong-thuy-gia-dinh-am-em-hinh-5.jpg\" alt=\"dat-tu-lanh-the-nao-cho-hop-phong-thuy-gia-dinh-am-em-hinh-5\" width=\"567\" height=\"425\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>V\u00ec th\u1ebf, n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed khu\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t t\u1ee7 l\u1ea1nh, nh\u01b0 v\u1eady v\u1eeba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m t\u0103ng t\u00e0i v\u1eadn, v\u1eeba h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t tho\u00e1t ti\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a.<\/p>\n<div><em>B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft mang t\u00ednh tham kh\u1ea3o.<\/em><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>\u0110\u1eb7t t\u1ee7 l\u1ea1nh \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed b\u1ea5t ti\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 g\u00e2y m\u1ea5t m\u1ef9 quan c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 b\u1ebfp m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn gia ch\u1ee7 theo phong th\u1ee7y. Hi\u1ec7n nay, h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 gia \u0111\u00ecnh n\u00e0o c\u0169ng c\u00f3 t\u1ee7 l\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng m\u00e0 n\u00f3 mang l\u1ea1i cho cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, &#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":3835,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[173,150,1],"tags":[162,181],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/tintuc6.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3834"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/tintuc6.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/tintuc6.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/tintuc6.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/tintuc6.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3834"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/tintuc6.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3834\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3836,"href":"https:\/\/tintuc6.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3834\/revisions\/3836"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/tintuc6.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3835"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/tintuc6.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3834"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href"